>> I have noted to the reset() clean up too much in the balancers:
>> mod_lbmethod_bybusyness.c for example does:
>> +++
>>      for (i = 0; i < balancer->workers->nelts; i++, worker++) {
>>          (*worker)->s->lbstatus = 0;
>>          ap_proxy_set_busy_count(*worker, 0); /* BAD */
